    "title": "Career Opportunity Medical Officer at Pfizer India",
    "description": "Pfizer India has an exciting opening for a Medical Officer at our Chennai office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Pfizer India:\nPfizer India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n• Maintain accurate clinical documentation in electronic health records\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Flexible working hours\n• Learning & development budget\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Pfizer India!",
